            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="meta-taskdescription" metaValue="You have to go in change mode of the order Co02 and then go to the operation overview...select the operation to want to release and press the button released. If you want collective release then to go for the CO05N transaction...select operations and profile and give the selection criteria...from here you can release the operations collectively."/>
